---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import BlogPost from '../../components/BlogPost.astro';

const breadcrumbs = [
  { text: 'Home', href: '/' },
  { text: 'Blog', href: '/blog' },
  { text: 'Forest Conservation Strategies', href: '/blog/forest-conservation-strategies' }
];
---

<BlogPost
  title="Forest Conservation Strategies"
  date="December 28, 2023"
  image={{
    src: "/images/forest.jpg",
    alt: "Forest conservation"
  }}
  breadcrumbs={breadcrumbs}
>
  <p>Forest conservation plays a crucial role in maintaining biodiversity and ensuring sustainable resource management. Modern conservation strategies combine traditional knowledge with innovative technologies.</p>

  <h2>Conservation Approaches</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Sustainable forestry practices</li>
    <li>Biodiversity monitoring systems</li>
    <li>Community-based conservation</li>
    <li>Reforestation programs</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Technology Integration</h2>
  <p>Modern forest conservation utilizes satellite monitoring, drone surveillance, and AI-powered analysis to track forest health and prevent illegal activities.</p>

  <h2>Economic Impact</h2>
  <p>Sustainable forest management creates economic opportunities through eco-tourism, carbon credits, and sustainable resource harvesting.</p>

  <h2>Future Outlook</h2>
  <p>Emerging trends include blockchain-based tracking systems, advanced remote sensing, and innovative conservation financing mechanisms.</p>
</BlogPost>